title: WordPress Themes Collection Jan 2014
description:
This is a collection of ~1700 assorted WordPress themes. Approx 200 of these are premium, the better/more popular themes from WordPress.org, and a variety collection from the interwebs. Popular frameworks are included in the _Frameworks directory. Simply copy the theme into your /wp-content/themes/ directory, active, and enjoy!

Please seed!

I was going to include the theme listing, but it was too long :(
